translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  4,27,"Soni Allah akusachilila kuti ampochele toba jenu, nambo ŵandu ŵaakukuya isako (yao) akusachililaga n'di mpombotele kupombotala kwekulungwa nnope"
  4,28,"Allah akusachilila kuti an'jepepachisye, pakuti mundu jwagumbidwe jwangali machili"
  4,29,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Kasillyaganilana chipanje chenu mwaukoleko, ikaŵeje gali malonda (gankusumana) mwakupikanganana chilikati chenu, soni ngasilliulaga mwachimisyene, chisimu Allah aŵele Jwachanasa kwa jemanja"
  4,30,"Soni jwachaiche mwakutenda yele mwakusumba mpika ni mwalupuso basi tuchija kun'jinjisya ku Moto, soni yalakweyo kwa Allah iŵele yakwepepala kusyene"
  4,31,"Naga n'diŵambasyeje (ilemwa) yekulungwakulungwa yankulekasyidwa, chitunsimachisye yakusakala yenu (yamwanamwana) ni tuchin'jinjisya kumalo kwauchimbichimbi (ku Mbepo)"
  4,32,"Soni ngasinyyilupataga ichindu yaapeleche Allah mwawinji kwa ŵane mwa jenumanja kwapunda ŵane, akwete kupata achalume liunjili lya (malipilo ga) yapanganyisye, nombe nao achakongwe akwete kupata liunjili lya (malipililo ga) yapanganyisye, ni mum'bendeje Allah ukoto Wakwe, chisimu Allah chindu chilichose aŵele Jwaachimanya chenene"
  4,33,"Soni kwa jwalijose (mwa jenumanja) tutomeche nkuntawalila (jwakwe) pa chipanje chalesile achinangolo ŵaŵili ni ŵaulongo, sano aŵala ŵamwataŵene nao chilanga (chakuntawalila chipanje chenu), mwapani liunjili lyao (kupitila mu wasiya wachimwalechele), chisimu Allah pa chindu chilichose aŵele Jwakutendela umboni"